| Category | Target |
|----------|--------|
| Domain logic (parsing, classification, aggregation) | ≥ 90% |
| Storage layer (SQLite operations) | ≥ 80% |
| API handlers | ≥ 80% |
| Platform-specific code (FFI wrappers) | Manual testing only |
| Configuration loading | ≥ 90% |

