## Console Logging Best Practices

### Structured Logging

```typescript
// Logger utility
const logger = {
  debug: (message: string, data?: unknown) => {
    if (import.meta.env.DEV) {
      console.log(`[DEBUG] ${message}`, data ?? '');
    }

  },

  info: (message: string, data?: unknown) => {
